Hemo bioscience - Project Current Work
Version: 0.6.5
Date: 2025-09-26

Current Task: Develop Annual Cost Analysis Report
Phase: 1 (Planning)

Goal: Implement the full logic and UI for the "Annual Cost Analysis" report, including data aggregation, summary metrics, a detailed table, and a flexible chart.

Key Objectives (this phase):

Develop a data aggregation function to collect all cost-related data for a given year.

Build the UI components to display the summary cards, the detailed breakdown table, and the flexible spend chart.

Wire the components into the generateReport function in the Reporting panel.

